<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>إِنْزَالُ الناس منازلهم <span class="c2">(٨٥٠٣ ــ ٨٥٠٥)</span> جـ <span class="c2">(٣)</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
